PhoneResult

data class PhoneResult(val skipped: Boolean, val phone: String?) : CollectInputsResult

PhoneResult contains data collected from a phone form

Parameters

skipped

if true, the skip button was pressed to skip the form.

phone

the submitted phone number in E.164 format. Null if the form was skipped.
